      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, there is no rhythm to find. it's just more of the same. even if i \"reached out,\" what would i even say? \"hey, i'm bored and lonely\"? it sounds so stupid. it's not like anyone actually cares about the person behind the screen, they just care that the tasks get done. if i disappeared, the tasks would just get reassigned. it's like i'm already gone, i'm just waiting for my body to catch up.",
